#

Braised Short Ribs with Creamy Polenta

200 min
$30
700 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 6

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh Protein

Cuisine:

AmericanItalian

Course:

Main CourseComfort Food

Tags:

Comfort FoodHeartyMain Course

Description

Tender, fall-off-the-bone short ribs paired with rich, creamy polenta for a cozy meal.

Ingredients

  • beef short ribs: 3 pounds
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • onion: 1, chopped
  • carrots: 2, chopped
  • celery: 2 stalks, chopped
  • garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • red wine: 1 cup
  • beef broth: 4 cups
  • bay leaves: 2
  • thyme: 1 teaspoon
  • polenta: 1 cup
  • butter: 2 tablespoons
  • parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup, grated
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
